Package org.apache.wiki.modules

Interface Summary
InternalModule This is a simple interface which is implemented by a number of JSPWiki components to signal that they should not be included in things like module listings and so on.
 

Class Summary
ModuleManager Superclass for all JSPWiki managers for modules (plugins, etc).
WikiModuleInfo A WikiModule describes whatever JSPWiki plugin there is: it can be a plugin, an editor, a filter, etc.
